(33, 9, 'Ecommerce and Logistics in West Africa', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><i><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\" face=\"times new roman\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Analyzing Ecommerce and Logistics in West Africa.</font></i></b></div><div><br><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:15.75pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">So what is Ecommerce?</font></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:15.75pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(32,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 36);\"=\"\">Electronic\r\ncommerce&nbsp;or&nbsp;e-commerce&nbsp;(sometimes written as&nbsp;eCommerce) is\r\na business model that lets firms and individuals buy and sell things over the\r\ninternet. Business to business. Business to consumer. Consumer to consumer.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:15.75pt\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(32,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 36);\"=\"\">What is Logistics and\r\nhow does it apply to Ecommerce?</span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(32,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 36);\"=\"\"><br></span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:15.75pt\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">As an ecommerce business owner, you\'ll have to familiarize\r\nyourself with logistics. Back-end supply chain management is a critical\r\ncomponent of any business today, but that\'s especially the case in ecommerce.\r\nSince you don\'t have a brick-and-mortar storefront to house inventory, you have\r\nto rely on third parties to help store and ship&nbsp;your products and\r\nservices. This is crucial for back time management&nbsp; and for\r\nyour&nbsp;bottom line.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br>\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">What is logistics?</span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n<font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Logistics is simply the\r\nmanagement of the way resources are obtained, stored and shipped to their end\r\ndestinations. The planning, execution and control of the movement and placement\r\nof these goods and services must all occur within a given system that\'s\r\ndesigned to achieve specific objectives, which may vary by industry.</span><br>\r\n<!--[endif]--><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Looking at Ecommerce and Logistics in West Africa</span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">\r\n\r\n</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Due to the progress made by the Information and Communication\r\nTechnologies (ICT), the world has become a global village with a new global\r\neconomy. The world economy is being continuously restructured, but the\r\neconomies of African nations have not benefited from this growth and\r\ndevelopment. Many researchers have advanced a variety of reasons why African,\r\nand other developing, countries lag behind in this revolution.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">However, not many have focused on the digital commerce aspects in\r\nECOWAS member countries, which is the primary focus of this article. Further,\r\nit is obvious that member countries of ECOWAS are seriously disadvantaged\r\nwithin the global economy<span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt\">.&nbsp;</span>African\r\nnations and ECOWAS countries in particular, must be better equipped to take\r\nadvantage of new technologies and new markets, which could help these countries\r\nto improve their socio&nbsp;economic&nbsp;conditions&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;&nbsp;achieve&nbsp;&nbsp;the\r\nSustainable Goals.</span><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:15.75pt\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Although there have been some significant changes and improvements\r\nin some aspects over the years in ECOWAS countries like Nigeria, Ghana, Liberia\r\nand Sierra Leon. The region has seen the rise of many eCommerce platforms\r\ncompeting among&nbsp;each other like Jumia, Konga, Tonaton, eShopAfrica,\r\nMagento etc.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">The failure of eCommerce companies and how unprofitable the sector\r\nhas been discussed at length. The&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">death of DealDey</span>&nbsp;and\r\nthe struggles of eCommerce giants like Konga and Jumia lend credence to these\r\nclaims.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Some companies decided to&nbsp;<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in\">move on from the sector</span>,\r\nand others continued the struggle for profitability, thus causing a rethink in\r\nbusiness models. Despite the odds, the resilience might be paying off as\r\neCommerce companies are getting more attention.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:15.75pt\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">In Nigeria, TradeDepot, with its unique B2B model,&nbsp;<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">has raised $13 million</span>&nbsp;in two years. In 2018,\r\nIbadan-based eCommerce startup, Foodlocker, averaged a&nbsp;<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">monthly revenue of $30,000</span>&nbsp;and has since reached more\r\nmilestones.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Away from Nigeria, Ghanaian&nbsp;EshopAfrica has seen a\r\nsignificant boost in its profit over the years, thanks to the new internet\r\nrevolution, while Ivorian eCommerce player, Afrikrea closed $1 Million in\r\nFebruary 2020.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);\"=\"\">Age Old Problem Persist&nbsp;</span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Companies like Jumia, Konga, DealDey, and Gloo started eCommerce\r\noperations when the Nigerian market was unfamiliar with online shopping;\r\nInternet penetration levels were low, and the logistics sector was not as\r\ndeveloped as it is today.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Statista’s report shows that Nigeria alone currently account for\r\n50% of online shoppers in West Africa seemingly points to a change in shopping\r\nculture. However, deep infrastructural and regulatory problems persist.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">For eCommerce and logistics companies, two principal problems\r\ninclude getting the required goods and finding the customers.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Ensuring The Right Deliveries</span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Ensuring a customer gets their order is complicated. The key to\r\nsolving this problem lies in the logistics and courier services space, but\r\nseveral issues make their services difficult.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">For one, most if not all ECOWAS countries street naming and house\r\nnumbering system still leave a lot to be desired. Even in major cities like\r\nLagos, Abuja, Accra, Kumasi, Abidjan, Conakry, it is always challenging to find\r\nsome streets, and when they’re found, sometimes houses are not numbered.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Surayyah Ahmad, CEO of Abuja-based YDS, explains that deliveries\r\nare typically done with the aid of WhatsApp, text messages, and phone calls.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">“We make sure the buyer can receive calls. When we get to a\r\nparticular landmark, we call, and they come out to meet our riders,” she\r\nexplains.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">For this, Surrayah makes sure their phones are recharged with\r\nadequate airtime for all the communication needed.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">In the commercial hub of Lagos,&nbsp;<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in\">Saudat Salami</span>, CEO of\r\nEasyshop, Easycook, has a similar story. Receive order, reach a landmark, and\r\ncall so the person can either give proper directions or come out to meet them.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">“We try to use Google Maps, but the Internet is not reliable all\r\nthe time, so we always make sure our drivers have enough airtime,” she adds.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Nigeria’s weak addressing system has an impact on eCommerce and\r\nseveral other services, such as healthcare and other essential deliveries,\r\nacross different sectors.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">This has been the purview of the Nigerian Postal Service (NIPOST).\r\nThe government agency also serves as the regulator for the logistics and\r\ncourier space in Nigeria.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">The Big Issues in Logistics</span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Speaking about the effectiveness of region’s addressing system,\r\nCourage, a small-scale fashion designer in Lagos Nigeria, says, “Things that\r\nwork smoothly in other countries don’t always work smoothly in Africa.”</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Aiki reflects that besides addressing, terrible roads and road\r\ndesigns are some of the biggest issues.</span> <span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Other players give some\r\ncontext.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Ahmad, a logistics driver in Accra Ghana argues that while it is\r\nuseful to have a more accurate addressing system, it doesn’t do much for\r\nirregular routes and sudden road closures.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">“Even with WhatsApp locations, you can get to a particular route\r\nand discover that it’s been closed or there’s no road there at all,” says\r\nAhmad.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">Although routes are slightly better in some West African cities\r\nsuch as Abuja, Lagos, Porto Novo, Cape Verde but still similar instances occur\r\nprobably because of the traffic congestion characteristic of the commercial\r\nhub.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">“When using Maps, it can direct you to go through an estate, and\r\nyou’ll meet the gates closed, or you could get caught on a one-way street,”\r\nSalami explains.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;\"=\"\">This is why logistics companies and drivers that understand the\r\nroutes are essential.</span><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"times new roman\" size=\"4\"><b style=\"\">How to Mitigate the Challenges of Ecommerce and Logistics&nbsp;in West Africa</b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">1. Refresh Policies</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"text-align: start;\">Policies shape the business environment, affecting everything from payment options to internet prices and IP protection. Yet Ecowas policies lag behind the rest of the world in some areas – for example, only few countries have rules for online consumer protection.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: left;\">Ecowas needs to have a mandated Digital Trade and Digital Economy Strategy to be developed&nbsp; to guide governments on multi-faceted e-commerce policy questions.</span><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-align: start;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">2. Expand Connectivity</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"text-align: left;\">Only a quarter of the region\'s population</span><span style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;regularly use the internet, and costs are high. Governments, business and international organisations should pour energy into the “missed” Sustainable Development Goal 9c to provide universal and affordable internet access to least developed countries by 2020. Committing to inclusive access across the region by 2030, this would boost domestic e-commerce growth and support entrepreneurship.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-align: start;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">&nbsp;</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-align: start;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">3. Upgrade Logistics</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><span style=\"text-align: start;\">Ecowas and donors can advance implementation of the World Trade Organization (WTO) Trade Facilitation Agreement (TFA) to reduce customs costs that eat into cross-border exchange, while public-private partnerships can deliver solutions for small business needs.</span><span style=\"text-align: start;\"><br></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">4. Join Force</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Capacity-building will be critical to ensuring that technology advances which will carry on globally regardless – are put to use for the region’s jobs and growth. To do so, increased donor support and public-private partnerships are needed to help with challenges unique to the region.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">5. Enable E-payments</font></p><div class=\"st__content-block st__content-block--text\" style=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.65rem;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Cash on delivery remains popular in the region, making cross-border e-commerce difficult. Also, policies are often not adapted to complex payment supply chains, meaning the region’s merchants have fewer options to connect their local e-payments systems with services used by global customers.</font></p></div><div class=\"st__content-block st__content-block--text\" style=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.65rem;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">Policy-makers need to work to improve local and global payment system interoperability. In so doing, bolstering the region’s position as a global leader in mobile payments to act as a first point of contact for universal financial services access.</font></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.65rem;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.65rem;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><b style=\"\">Conclusion</b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">E-commerce in West Africa can\r\nbe improved by bridging the digital divide through regulatory reform. The basic\r\nIC infrastructure necessary to support eﬃcient e-commerce can be developed and\r\nimproved by opening up all aspects of the region’s telecommunications sector to\r\ncompetitors. These investors have the ﬁnancial force to absorb the high cost of\r\nICT development and if well-regulated could further have a competitive interest\r\nin providing quality telecommunications services. Therefore, regulating for\r\nmarket liberalization would set the pace for development of ICT infrastructure\r\nin the region’s struggling economies. In addition, government involvement is\r\nnecessary for promoting ICT awareness and conﬁdence.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><font face=\"times new roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\">In addition, governments needs to invest more in infrastructure such as roads, road signs and house numbering to ease and aid logistics.</font></span></p></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"><font face=\"times new roman\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"><br></span></p></div></div>', '1612275901retail-e-commerce-logistics-main.jpg', 'https://techpoint.africa/ https://www.practicalecommerce.com/ https://www.researchgate.net/  https://www.weforum.org/', 100, 1, 'Ecommerce and Logistics in West Africa', 'Analyzing in-depth the Key Challenges of Ecommerce and Logistics in West Africa', 'Challenges and Solutions of Ecommerce and Logistics in West Africa', '2021-02-02 19:08:40');
