able shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We don’t guarantee that we will receive your returned item.</div>', 1, 85, 'SPAGHETTI', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '0', 0, 'Golden Penny Spaghetti', 'Golden Penny Spaghetti is a long, thin, dried cylindrical pasta that is very tasty, does not get soggy and is enjoyed in a variety of ways and cooks in ten minutes. ... Golden Penny Spaghetti can be enjoyed plain with stew, vegetables, as Jollof or fried. It is very tasty and does not get soggy.', NULL, 'Physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2020-10-27 15:38:32', '2021-11-23 06:14:47', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
